             DIVISION 05 — MECHANICAL WORKS  (authoritative complete source)
             الأعمال الميكانيكية

             This file is the single source of truth for Division 05.
             It is loaded LAST among work-structure data files so that:
               - All previously loaded subdivision / sub-subdivision records
                 already exist in the DB and can be safely updated or
                 deactivated here.
               - Every record is written with noupdate="0", guaranteeing
                 a clean, canonical state after every module upgrade.

             Load order (manifest):
               farm_division_work_data.xml
               farm_subdivision_work_data.xml
               farm_sub_subdivision_work_data.xml
               farm_div05_mechanical_complete.xml   ← this file
        ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->


